Soulpowerr BluesCrooner- 3*, Troll Skald, MLF<br>
Dzugu PrisonShank- 22nd, Kobold SB, MLF<br>
Pimplap SpazzOut 11th, Dwarf Berzerker, MLF <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udimuyensylvanesty.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dimuyen Sylvanesty</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/24/02 11:50:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dealing With Smite Clerics</span><hr size=1> Cleric mezz doesn't have ZZzzz for an effect. It's a green/red light thingy. <p>Dimuyen 43 Armsman<BR>
